{
  "stem": "1496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Russian army came, coming closer, and Schindler--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, because they-- they didn't want the survivors or prisoners, they didn't want to leave behind.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, they thought they might need them for some other work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And second thing, they didn't want to show what they were doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't want any witnesses, right after the Russian army took over Poland, Krakow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't want to bring to open what they were doing, how they were killing innocent people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we felt-- already by rumors, we heard it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they said you have to be evacuated, we knew that what was the reason.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A group of people-- I was included in them-- were left behind.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to disassemble the munition part of the factory, put the heavy machinery on a train, and we sent them to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Rest of the-- and after we completed this job, we were also sent back to Krakau-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually, we were in Plaszow for a short time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just a few days.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They loaded us in the cattle cars, and they sent us away to Gross Rosen concentration camp, Gross Rosen in Germany, the 700 men.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's the time where Schindler's List was actually established, when all the people, the 700 men and 300 women, went back to Krakau-Plaszow, to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schindler worked very hard and tried very hard to get his 1,000 people, 700 men and 300 women, back to Czechoslovakia, when he will reestablish the munition factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Under the-- he was selling-- his selling point was that we are already professional.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are trained.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We know what to do, how to produce the munition.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's the reason, he said, I want my 1,000 people to be transferred to Brnenec, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he succeeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
